1.0 Whom does the policy cover?
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
The holder of a valid MasterCard Gold card (excluding family cards) issued
by &BANKNAVN., as well as his/her spouse/life partner who is travelling
with him/her:
.of 5mm
*¤The cardholder's partner must live at the same address as the cardholder
to be included in the coverage.
.of 0mm
.of 5mm
*¤The cardholder's spouse is covered, even though he/she may not live at
the same address as the cardholder.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Any children of the cardholder and his/her spouse/partner are covered
according to the following rules, when such children are travelling
together with the cardholder:
.of 5mm
*¤Children of the cardholder and his/her spouse/partner are covered up
until the age of 21, irrespective of their address.
.of 5mm
*¤Children of the cardholder and his/her spouse/partner are covered
when said children share the same official address as the
cardholder, irrespective of their age.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In this context, 'life partner' is taken to mean a person who lives with
the cardholder in a marriage-like relationship, and who, for at least six
months prior to the insurance event, has shared an address with the
cardholder.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
1.1 The insurance coverage also applies if the cardholder has a MasterCard
Gold card and lives abroad.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
months. If the insured has neither a spouse nor a life partner,
payment will be made to his/her children.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If the insured does not have a spouse/partner or children, the sum payable
on death is limited to DKK 12,000.
.sp 3mm
