4.0 Travel accident insurance
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.br
Insurance sum payable on death: DKK 750,000 per person.
.br
Insurance sum payable on disability: DKK 750,000 per person.
.br
Insurance sum payable on the death of persons aged under 18: DKK 20,000
per person.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
4.1 Coverage
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance covers death or medical disability as well as dental
damage resulting from an accident, taken to mean a sudden incident that
causes personal injury.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
4.2 Compensation
:SKRSLUT.
.br
4.2.1 The right to receive compensation for death exists when an
accident has led to death within one year of the date of the
injury. The sum payable on death is DKK 750,000. The sum payable on
the death of persons under the age of 18 is DKK 20,000. If
disability compensation has been paid in connection with the same
accident, the sum paid will be deducted from the sum paid on death.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
4.2.2 Disability compensation is payable when an accident has resulted
in permanent medical disability of at least 5%, and the condition is
stationary. Compensation is payable up to three years from the date of
the injury. If the condition is not stationary at this time, the
compensation payable will be determined on the basis of the condition
at this time, irrespective of whether the condition becomes stationary
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
6.0 Payment of compensation
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
Privatsikring's ordinary means of payment is by bank
transfer. Privatsikring therefore requires details of the
relevant bank and account number in order to be able to pay
compensation.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
However, compensation may be paid by check on payment of a fee that
will be deducted from the compensation paid.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Compensation sums payable to children under the age of 18 will be paid
in accordance with the provisions concerning funds for minors.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
