8.0 Double insurance
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
In the event that double insurance exists, Privatsikring shall only
provide coverage to the extent that the insured is not covered by
another party.
.br
In the event of travel accidents (Section B, 4.0), the insurance shall
provide full coverage, irrespective of coverage by another party.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
Recourse
:SKRSLUT.
.br
In the event of payments made pursuant to the present
policy, Privatsikring is to enter into the insured's rights
in this regard.
